{"tid":1479254,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"紅土shopping地圖分析(一)","createTime":"2019-08-16T22:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T05:55:27.000Z","uid":61002,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"99f897d48ec15d6b48af0bb1b8d7f2b1d087d529","tid":1479254,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T22:40:14.000Z","msg":"首先多謝大家咁熱烈支持旅遊業，喺呢個咁艱難嘅時刻都毫不猶豫去促進本地經濟。<br />\n但大家都要了解到九龍城區呢個舊區就，其實好依賴陸上交通(巴士小巴)，因為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">地鐵兜大圈而沙中綫未開通</span></span><br />\n所以返工放工rush hour經常見到咁嘅情形<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ndnv7WY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdnv7WY.png&h=6dcad4ca&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z8X0LJK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz8X0LJK.png&h=e4d13cb8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qcfxBQv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqcfxBQv.png&h=faad3884&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RjfBi3Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRjfBi3Z.png&h=6d095aeb&s={SIZE}\" /> 好話唔好聽分分鐘係吞吐緊成個東西九龍加過海交通個容量㗎每日<br />\n所以唔想嘥時間塞車的團友就記得自己預返時間日期啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外就係呢一區舊樓私樓最多，尤其對正大馬路，冇看更都有大閘，至於地下都係一啲街坊鋪頭同食肆。想搵商場行下涼下冷氣都係得kcp呀翔龍灣或者紅磡廣場，一係就去到黃埔先叫做多嘢行。所以就更加冇咩<span style=\"font-size: large;\">高架天橋</span>或者隧道咁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ptSBS6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ptSBS6.jpg&h=e87c3624&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁若然閣下不幸有咩頭暈身㷫需要call消防救護睇醫生，除咗就近家庭醫生，都可以call白車咁，或者幫到手，但記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">千祈唔好濫用救護服務</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OBHv70s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBHv70s.png&h=44e64d7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果行行下街遇上罪案，有需要尋求香港警察嘅協助，但999又唔通的話，都可以考慮下親身上門報驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TxmHY73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTxmHY73.png&h=281696e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又或者你打完999但唔知警車幾時先到，可能以下估計出沒點/方向可以安撫到你不安的心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a38bSt5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa38bSt5.jpg&h=d603c6ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">祝各位購物愉快!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461298b0f216c672d18c730aa2a42e7c1d122a24","tid":1479254,"uid":79836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T22:46:32.000Z","msg":"<strong>今日三半紅土遊行，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">竟然連一個熱門Post都無？！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅土遊行！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不是CONDOM！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">817塞爆紅土！！！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n818塞爆維園！！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">延伸閱讀：</span></strong><br />\n教你點樣去土瓜灣 海心公園<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478800</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1cedcb0cb85c006b7c7080bf6d3b37c8d2ae965","tid":1479254,"uid":82587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T22:47:35.000Z